<feed xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><title>边缘 - 所有帖子</title><icon>https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/community_logos/52801/VER_Logomark_32x32..png</icon><updated> 2024-09-27T11:29:47-04:00</updated><id> https://www.theverge.com/rss/full.xml</id><link href="https://www.theverge.com/" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><entry><published> 2024-09-27T11:29:47-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T11:29:47-04:00</updated><title>现在，Google Flights 上的搜索也会建议乘坐 Amtrak 火车</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Amtrak 列车在轨道上，背景是水体&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/7GYfva8VptChOsV8peVRq3Cvm4w=/62x0:2498x1624/1310x873/cdn.vox -cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73615389/2014_0624_ACS64_BushRiverBridgeIMG_2657_scaled.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;火车很酷，但乘坐起来并不总是便宜。&lt;/em>; |图片：Amtrak&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;ei7O2D&quot;>;Amtrak 票价和行程建议 &lt;a href=&quot;https://media.amtrak.com/2024/09/amtrak-debuts-new-integration -with-google-to-support-more-sustainable-transportation-choices/&quot;>;正在集成到 Google 搜索&lt;/a>;中，作为 Google 努力提供更环保的航班旅行方式的一部分。现在，当您在 Google 或 Google Flights 上搜索往返于 Amtrak 航站楼的目的地之间的机票时，您还会收到有关火车行程的建议，您可以点击这些建议前往 Amtrak 网站进行购买。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;B3cKiR&quot; >;Google &lt;a href=&quot;https://blog.google/outreach-initiatives/sustainability/google-transportation-energy-emissions-reduction/&quot;>;一直在&lt;/a>;致力于&lt;a href=&quot;https:// blog.google/products/search/find-more-sustainable-ways-to-get-around-with-new-maps-and-search-updates/&quot;>;暂时提供可持续交通&lt;/a>;选项，以及它之前曾显示过火车乘车建议，但没有票价，也没有轻松重定向到 Amtrak 网站来购买特定车票 - 尽管我每次尝试时它都不起作用。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;VE3Hyf&quot;>; Google 还会计算乘坐火车前往目的地时可节省多少碳排放量。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255817/google -search-flights-amtrak-train-suggestions-tickets&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255817/google-search-flights-amtrak-train-suggestions-tickets" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255817/google-search-flights-amtrak-train-suggestions-tickets</id><author><name>奥马尔·沙基尔</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-27T11:22:42-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T11:22:42-04:00</updated><title>最适合您 iPhone 的 MagSafe 和 Qi2 充电器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;各种 MagSafe 充电器的照片拼贴。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/2w7Phksq07lEVBqIRIJ_oasnPkg=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/71769681/247290_Buying_Guide_MagSafe_Charger_CVirginia。 6.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p>;感谢 Qi2，为您的 MagSafe 手机提供比以往更多的优质充电器。&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/23505846/best-magsafe-magnet-chargers-apple-iphone&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/23505846/best-magsafe-magnetic-chargers-apple-iphone" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/23505846/best-magsafe-magnet-chargers-apple-iphone</id><author><name>安东尼奥·G·迪·贝内代托</name><name>内森·爱德华兹</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-27T10:51:30-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T10:51:30-04:00</updated><title> Steam 现在可以让你起诉 Valve</title><content type="html"> &lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;粉红色背景上的 Steam 标志，周围环绕着 Valve 标志。&quot; src =“https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/bZhbBwX-hMHWL-eOW65SnPtnaTo=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73615255/STK139_Stream_Kradtke_01.0。 jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;urNIkS&quot;>;Steam 刚刚取消了强制仲裁政策，为其母公司 Valve 提起诉讼打开了大门。在&lt;a href=&quot;https://steamcommunity.com/games/593110/announcements/detail/4696781406111167992?utm_source=SteamDB&quot;>;周四的更新&lt;/a>;中，Steam 表示&lt;a href=&quot;https://store .steampowered.com/subscriber_agreement?snr=2_groupannouncements_detail_#10&quot;>;其订户协议&lt;/a>;“现在规定任何争议均应提交法庭而不是仲裁。”&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;Mo4CY6&quot;>;许多公司在其用户协议中包含强制仲裁条款，放弃个人在法庭上受审的权利。仲裁涉及在公正的第三方面前解决法律体系之外的争议。这种方法通常速度更快，但可能无法为消费者获得最佳结果，因为仲裁员 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.consumeradvocates.org/for-consumers/ Arbitration/#:~:text=Arbitration%20is%20a% 20private%20system%20without%20a%20judge%2C%20jury%2C%20or%20a%20right%20to%20an%20上诉。%C2%A0Arbitrators%20aren%27t%20required%20to%20take%20the%20law%20and%20legal %20先例%20进入%20帐户%20在%20中做出%20他们的%20决定。%20那里%20是%20没有%20上诉%20或%20公开%20审查%20的%20决定%20到%20确保%20%20仲裁员%20得到%20it%20权利。&quot;>;做出决定时不需要考虑法律&lt;/a>;。&lt;/p>; &lt;div class=&quot;c-float-left c-float-hang&quot;>;&lt;aside id=&quot;ZpH7Ex&quot;>;&lt;div data- anthem-component=&quot;readmore&quot; data-anthem-component-data=&#39;{&quot;stories&quot;:[{&quot;title&quot;:&quot;迪士尼希望因迪士尼+协议而驳回非正常死亡诉讼&quot;,&quot;url&quot;:&quot;https ://www.theverge.com/2024/8/14/24220228/disney-wrongful-death-lawsuit-subscription-terms&quot;}]}&#39;>;&lt;/div>;&lt;/aside>;&lt;/div>; &lt;p id= &quot;4Kcyk4&quot;>;许多服务将强制性仲裁协议纳入其服务条款中，&lt;a href=&quot;https://papers.ssrn.com/sol3/papers.cfm?abstract_id=4521064&quot;>;人们甚至可能没有阅读或完全阅读该协议...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255841/steam-forced- Arbitration-policy-lawsuit&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip ;&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255841/steam-forced-arbitration-policy-lawsuit" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255841/steam-forced- Arbitration-policy-lawsuit</id><author><name>艾玛·罗斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-27T09:03:09-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T09:03:09-04:00</updated><title> Meta 的新型智能眼镜看起来就像未来</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Meta Connect 的照片，位于 Vergecast 插图上。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/0bh9wfkkzJA0ACufKzimVNO17lE=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73615011/VST_0928_Site.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Alex Parkin / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;uO1Oo3&quot;>;你买不到 Meta 最令人印象深刻的新产品，代号 Orion 的智能眼镜。几年后你也许可以买到类似的东西，但我们大多数人永远不会穿它们。但这并不一定会使它们不那么令人印象深刻，或者不那么重要。 Orion 是 Meta 的目标声明：AR 眼镜确实是未来，我们最终会实现这一目标。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;wq2J8x&quot;>;On &lt;a href=&quot;https://link .chtbl.com/vergecast&quot;>;这一集&lt;em>;The Vergecast&lt;/em>;&lt;/a>;，&lt;em>;The Verge&lt;/em>;的&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com /authors/alex-heath&quot;>;Alex Heath&lt;/a>; 加入节目，向我们讲述&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24253908/meta-orion-ar-glasses-demo-mark -zuckerberg-interview&quot;>;他与 Orion 的经历&lt;/a>;——在未来的眼镜中度过两个小时，与 Meta 首席执行官马克·扎克伯格一起打乒乓球，制作冰沙并做各种其他事情。他还向我们讲述了&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24253481/meta-ceo-mark-zuckerberg-ar-glasses-orion-ray-bans-ai-decoder-interview&quot;>;他与扎克伯格...&lt;/a>;&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255557/meta-orion-quest-smart-glasses-ar- connect-vergecast&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255557/meta-orion-quest-smart-glasses-ar-connect-vergecast" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255557/meta-orion-quest-smart-glasses-ar-connect-vergecast</id><author><name>大卫·皮尔斯</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-27T08:13:54-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T08:13:54-04:00</updated><title> LG 和 Razer 为云游戏打造了超灵敏蓝牙控制器</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;在 LG webOS 峰会上拍摄的 Razer 新型支持 ULL 的蓝牙控制器的照片&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/Tum3VklfCRUjE8wliCytmTXzlyg=/33x0:1887x1236/1310x873/ cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73614885/Razer_LG_BT_ULL_controller.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;新的支持 ULL 的控制器（见右图）针对未指定的标准蓝牙游戏手柄（左图）进行了测试).&lt;/em>; |图片：LG&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;3Lvth0&quot;>;LG 与 Razer 和 MediaTek 合作开发&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.lgnewsroom.com/2024/09/lg-与雷蛇和联发科合作推出有史以来首个蓝牙超低延迟技术/&quot;>;一款新的蓝牙游戏控制器&lt;/a>;，可以大大减少云的输入延迟基于游戏。据 LG 称，它是第一个利用超低延迟 (ULL) 蓝牙技术的控制器 - &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.bluetooth.com/specations/specifications-in-development/#:~:text= Ultra%20Low%20Latency%20HID&quot;>;正在开发的标准&lt;/a>;，旨在使无线控制器与有线控制器一样灵敏。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;38FNi7&quot;>;对支持 BT ULL 的控制器进行了比较周五，LG 在 webOS 峰会上与“标准控制器”展开了较量。 LG 在其新闻编辑室帖子中表示：“此次演示凸显了 BT ULL 技术在各种基于云的游戏（包括 FPS、格斗和赛车游戏）中的卓越响应能力、减少的输入延迟和控制精度。”&lt;/p>; &lt;figure class= &quot;e-image&quot;>; &lt;cite>;图片：LG&lt;/cite>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;有...&lt;/em>;&lt;/figcaption>;&lt;/figure>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https:// www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255778/lg-razer-ultra-low-latency-bluetooth-ull-gaming-controller&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255778/lg-razer-ultra-low-latency-bluetooth-ull-gaming-controller" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255778/lg-razer-ultra-low-latency-bluetooth-ull-gaming-controller</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-27T05:29:23-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-27T05:29:23-04:00</updated><title> Gemini 正在让 Gmail 的智能回复变得更加智能</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Gmail 徽标的插图。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/mrflUO5TaFazXhLcKegcETBIqWA=/0x0:3000x2000/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73614644/acastro_STK459_11.0.jpg&quot;/>; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;Gmail 中的自动回复现在可以为 iOS 和 Android 上的某些用户提供更多详细信息和上下文。&lt;/em>; |插图由 Alex Castro / The Verge &lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;xURMtU&quot;>;Google 正在针对 Android 和 iOS 版 Gmail 推出由 Gemini 驱动的更新，该更新将为电子邮件量身定制智能回复。首先&lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/5/14/24156500/google-gmail-ai-gemini-summaries-contextual-smart-reply&quot;>;于 5 月份宣布&lt;/a>;， &lt;a href=&quot;https://workspaceupdates.googleblog.com/2024/09/contextual-smart-replies.html&quot;>;Google 表示&lt;/a>;其新的上下文智能回复将“提供更详细的回复，以充分捕捉意图” ”，考虑电子邮件线程的全部内容。&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;7F9wOS&quot;>;用户可以将鼠标悬停在每个建议的上下文智能回复上以预览文本，然后选择最适合的选项符合他们的需求或写作风格。可以立即编辑或发送建议的回复。我们的想法是，这既可以节省时间（尤其是当您经常埋头于 Gmail 收件箱时），又可以改善可用的自动回复的多样性，而不仅仅是简单的“是的，...”&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href= “https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255722/google-gemini-gmail-contextual-smart-replies-availability&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255722/google-gemini-gmail-contextual-smart-replies-availability" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/27/24255722/google-gemini-gmail-contextual-smart-replies-availability</id><author><name>杰西韦瑟贝德</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T19:00:00-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T19:00:00-04:00</updated><title>这款 Eufy 安全摄像头可以像白天一样显示夜间</title><content type="html">&lt;图>; &lt;img alt=&quot;&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/8sECWcgJe7Aqro8sBDTfQhoCzJc=/910x333:4367x2638/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73614018 /eufyCam_S3_Pro___Intruder_image.0.jpeg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;&lt;em>;EufyCam S3 Pro 安全摄像头具有内置聚光灯，但也可以显示夜间镜头，就像没有聚光灯的白天一样。&lt;/em>; |图片：Eufy&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&quot;e5ynRO&quot;>;来自 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https 的最新安全摄像头%3A%2F%2Fwww.eufy.com%2F&amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F26%2F24255217%2Feufycam-s3-pro-smart-security -camera-night-vision-apple-home&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;Eufy&lt;/a>; - Anker 的智能家居公司 - 可以在黑暗中清晰可见，使用雷达运动感应来减少误报，并在接线时 24/7 进行记录。与其他 Eufy 摄像机一样，新款 S3 Pro 提供免费的面部识别、包裹、车辆和宠物检测，以及本地存储的录制视频，无需按月付费。 &lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;81F4w0&quot;>;与大多数其他 Eufy 相机不同，S3 Pro 可与 Apple Home 配合使用，并与 &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/24074904/smart-home 兼容-camera-security-privacy-how-to#:~:text=Safe%20and%20simple%3A%20Apple%E2%80%99s%20HomeKit%20Secure%20Video%C2%A0&quot;>;Apple 的 HomeKit 安全视频服务&lt;/ a>;.&lt;/p>; &lt;p id=&quot;GmsaHR&quot;>;&lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id=66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eufy .com%2F&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024%2F9%2F26%2F24255217%2Feufycam-s3-pro-smart-security-camera-night-vision-apple -home&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;EufyCam S3 Pro&lt;/a>; 本周作为两摄像头捆绑包推出，其中一台 &lt;a href=&quot;https://go.redirectingat.com?id =66960X1514734&amp;amp;xs=1&amp;amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.eufy.com%2Fproducts%2Ft80301d1%3Fvariant%3D41846278357178&amp;amp;referrer=theverge.com&amp;amp;sref=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theverge.com%2F2024 %2F9%2F26%2F24255217%2Feufycam-s3-pro-smart-security-camera-night-vision-apple-home&quot; rel=&quot;owned nofollow noopener&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;>;HomeBase S380&lt;/a>; 售价 549.99 美元。 HomeBase 3 支持智能警报和本地存储（16GB 板载存储，可扩展至 16TB）。它还将 S3 Pro 连接到 Apple Home，使其成为首款 Eufy 相机...&lt;/p>; &lt;p>; &lt;a href=&quot;https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24255217/ eufycam-s3-pro-smart-security-camera-night-vision-apple-home&quot;>;继续阅读&amp;hellip;&lt;/a>; &lt;/p>; </content><link href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24255217/eufycam-s3-pro-smart-security-camera-night-vision-apple-home" rel="alternate" type="text/html"/><id> https://www.theverge.com/2024/9/26/24255217/eufycam-s3-pro-smart-security-camera-night-vision-apple-home</id><author><name>詹妮弗·帕蒂森·图伊</name></author></entry><entry><published>2024-09-26T18:37:58-04:00</published><updated> 2024-09-26T18:37:58-04:00</updated><title>亚马逊 10 月 Prime Day 活动 The Verge 指南</title><content type="html">&lt;figure>; &lt;img alt=&quot;Prime Big Deal Days 各种促销产品的图形照片拼贴。&quot; src=&quot;https://cdn.vox-cdn.com/thumbor/ISATRykm-j8_76CJO_rmNK0HJII=/0x0:2040x1360/1310x873/cdn.vox-cdn.com/uploads/chorus_image/image/73613962/247273_Prime_Big_Deals_Days_2024_CVirgin ia_PACKAGE.0.jpg&quot; />; &lt;figcaption>;图片：Cath Virginia / The Verge&lt;/figcaption>; &lt;/figure>; &lt;p id=&qu